- [ ] ScanResultsTable renders using rich_rust Table
- [ ] StatsTable renders using rich_rust Table
- [ ] PackListTable renders using rich_rust Table
- [ ] Progress indicators use rich_rust ProgressBar
- [ ] Markdown table output still works (--format markdown)
- [ ] Column widths adapt to terminal width
